	   <tr><td colspan=2>I am a Shadow Knight and I feel that it is pointless to use your pets. Save your mana for Spells. I would suggest using Siphon Strength spell to pull your enemies and If your solo use a good combination of DOTs and Sapping Spells. Since you are a tank I think that you do not need a pet cause you can wear heavy armor and take alot of hits.<br>&nbsp;<br>I am Iguanicus TheLizard of Tunare Server</td></tr>
